name: Anastasia Papadopoulos
summary:
Anastasia Papadopoulos, a 29-year-old woman, is seeking a long-term, monogamous relationship. She works as a Content Strategy Manager in the marketing industry and is a graduate of New York University. Based in Los Angeles, Anastasia is originally from Athens, Greece. She speaks English, Greek, and Spanish, and her key values are creativity, independence, and compassion. 

Regarding her interests, Anastasia enjoys painting, traveling, and yoga. She identifies as a liberal and practices the Orthodox faith. Anastasia is a straight white Caucasian woman with Scorpio as her zodiac sign, and she identifies as an ENFJ, according to the MBTI personality scale.

She does not smoke or use marijuana or other drugs. She does, however, consume alcohol occasionally and maintains an active lifestyle. Anastasia does not have children but wants to have them in the future. She has a cat as a pet and prefers a partner in the age range of 30 to 36 years who shares similar interests and values. Her desired partner would ideally not have children yet but is open to having children in future. They should also lead an active lifestyle and not smoke, use marijuana or other drugs. Responsible alcohol consumption is acceptable.
